file 2

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lasagna</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Lasagna</h1>
    <img src="lasagna.jpg" alt="Delicious lasagna">
    <h2>Description</h2>
    <p>This lasagna recipe features layers of tender pasta, rich meat sauce, and creamy béchamel for the ultimate comfort food.</p>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Lasagna noodles</li>
        <li>Ground beef</li>
        <li>Tomato sauce</li>
        <li>Ricotta cheese</li>
        <li>Mozzarella cheese</li>
        <li>Parmesan cheese</li>
        <li>Garlic</li>
        <li>Onion</li>
        <li>Olive oil</li>
        <li>Salt and pepper</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Steps</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Preheat the oven to 375°F (190°C).</li>
        <li>Cook lasagna noodles according to package instructions.</li>
        <li>Prepare the meat sauce by sautéing garlic and onion, then adding ground beef and tomato sauce.</li>
        <li>Layer the lasagna noodles, meat sauce, and cheeses in a baking dish.</li>
        <li>Bake for 40 minutes or until bubbly and golden.</li>
    </ol>
</body>
</html>

file 3

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Pancakes</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Pancakes</h1>
    <img src="pancakes.jpg" alt="Fluffy pancakes">
    <h2>Description</h2>
    <p>Fluffy, golden pancakes perfect for breakfast. Easy to make and a hit for the entire family!</p>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>1 cup all-purpose flour</li>
        <li>2 tablespoons sugar</li>
        <li>1 teaspoon baking powder</li>
        <li>1/2 teaspoon baking soda</li>
        <li>1/4 teaspoon salt</li>
        <li>3/4 cup milk</li>
        <li>1 egg</li>
        <li>2 tablespoons melted butter</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Steps</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Mix the dry ingredients in a bowl.</li>
        <li>In a separate bowl, whisk together milk, egg, and melted butter.</li>
        <li>Combine wet and dry ingredients until just mixed.</li>
        <li>Heat a non-stick skillet over medium heat and pour batter to form pancakes.</li>
        <li>Cook until bubbles form and flip to cook the other side.</li>
    </ol>
</body>
</html>

file 4

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Spaghetti</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Spaghetti</h1>
    <img src="spaghetti.jpg" alt="Delicious spaghetti">
    <h2>Description</h2>
    <p>This classic spaghetti dish is a simple yet delicious combination of pasta and tomato-based sauce, topped with herbs and Parmesan.</p>
    <h2>Ingredients</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Spaghetti pasta</li>
        <li>Tomato sauce</li>
        <li>Ground beef or meatballs</li>
        <li>Garlic</li>
        <li>Onion</li>
        <li>Olive oil</li>
        <li>Parmesan cheese</li>
        <li>Salt and pepper</li>
        <li>Fresh basil</li>
    </ul>
    <h2>Steps</h2>
    <ol>
        <li>Boil the spaghetti pasta according to the package instructions.</li>
        <li>Prepare the sauce by sautéing garlic and onion in olive oil.</li>
        <li>Add ground beef or meatballs and cook until browned.</li>
        <li>Pour in the tomato sauce and simmer for 15 minutes.</li>
        <li>Mix the pasta with the sauce and top with Parmesan and basil.</li>
    </ol>
</body>
</html>
